data.description: Stop your search, and welcome this two story house to market!  Your new home features four bedrooms/two bathrooms, a one car garage, in a gated community!  Pull up to curb appeal and enter to an inviting living area.  The kitchen and dining areas have lots of cabinet and cooking space, with plenty of room for entertaining!  Head upstairs to all four bedrooms!  The primary bedroom/bathroom are sizable, and include double sinks, and walk-in closet!  The backyard is private and quiet.  No carpets throughout house!  Community features also include a clubhouse, dog park, pool, and more!  Conveniently located to all highway and shopping need!  Come on by while this one lasts!
